rComments: This class was great, especially that we got to go to Europe. Yes, the classes before the trip are quite extensive, but you do need them in order to be able to discuss topics with lecturers in Europe. Anil knew the importance of attending all of our appointments in Europe but also to enjoy ourselves. There was only a paper due at the end.
